    <div data-cid="1795755">
        <div class="main review-item" id="1795755">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2528662/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2528662-30.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2528662/" class="name">豪仔</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2009-03-05" class="main-meta">2009-03-05 17:42:10</span>


            <span class="publisher right">
                <a class="publisher" target="_blank" href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1347194/">木馬2005版</a>
            </span>
    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1795755/">繼秋葉原@DEEP後又一震撼我的石田衣良出品</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1795755_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1795755">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        首先要知道小弟是一個很執著完滿的人。系列書籍當然要由一到二，再慢慢開展下去。大概就是閱讀一個人，開始認識，了解一點點，知道他/她的性格，想要知道他/她的近況。當然沒錯，那個人就是真島誠吧！  回想起池袋西口公園系列一，故事越後越發刺激。暴力、血腥、多少情色的描...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1795755-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1795755_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1795755_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1795755" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-1795755">
                                2
                        </span>
